scene.message:
Nanjo: {ctl0f:1}, if you've{nl}
gotten scared, you're free{nl}
to go home.{waitkey}I'll defeat him even on{nl}
my own!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Sonomura feels like{nl}
her personality's changed{nl}
somehow...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: We've stuck our necks{nl}
into something tremendous,{nl}
haven't we.{wait_fr:32} It's getting{nl}
interesting!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: My arms are itching{nl}
for action! Hurry up and let{nl}
me cut loose!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, hey, we're just{nl}
high schoolers, right?{waitkey}They wouldn't, like, go bang!{nl}
with guns at us...{wait_fr:32} not even{nl}
SEBEC would, right?{waitkey}{ret}
